{"tid":1647674,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"記唔記得我地個初衷？ 我地一開始就諗過靠美國幫手咩？","createTime":"2019-10-12T00:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:37:22.000Z","uid":6111,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5a02e9729e1a66dfddb52e70c548e30a3f1e1874","tid":1647674,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:31:05.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解要咁驚？<br />\n由6.9開始既第一日我地根本就冇諗過會有外國人幫我地<br />\n果陣我地一直都係抱住唔撤就攬炒既心態出去抗爭<br />\n直到美國出現大家就開始放軟手腳打晒飛機咁<br />\n到依家侵侵出聲你地就淆撚晒底咁做乜？<br />\n冇人幫手我地咪還原基本步 攬炒囉<br />\n反正我地輸左都係會被清算<br />\n咁被清算前我地會唔會乜都唔做呀<br />\n唔會呀屌你 記住一個說話<br />\n我地唔係羔羊 所以我地唔會坐以待斃<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒</span></span>"},{"pid":"badb320db3235d39b83b474908a679a83264f914","tid":1647674,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:34:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒</span></span>"},{"pid":"a628fedb496670e03223ff79e199155cd4cf3437","tid":1647674,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:36:25.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒"},{"pid":"05729341f6608a68509098357b9301573674b057","tid":1647674,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:38:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒</span></span>"},{"pid":"5f9a122d7a4412240355a62dc3fa2b6c6cd716bc","tid":1647674,"uid":123497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:40:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒</span></div></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0f14049a8bde34fb4bd0a425adc67c3fa6dac399","tid":1647674,"uid":6111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:44:25.000Z","msg":"美國唔幫手我地係咪唔洗幫班受害既手足呀？<br />\n我地係咪睇住佢地死既死 傷既傷呀？<br />\n我地依班安好既人係咪要繼續靠人幫呀？<br />\n我地一定要贏 我地要贏靠既就只可以係自己同身邊果個手足<br />\n醒啦香港人 我定就算輸都唔可以輸得咁難睇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">寧為玉碎 不為瓦全</span></span>"},{"pid":"664f536dabbfd316363c20be265289b0286d0cdf","tid":1647674,"uid":6111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:50:14.000Z","msg":"係咪黨鐵一封就有藉口比自己去唔到遊行？<br />\n有冇諗過搞機場果幾次呀？<br />\n班手足冇黨鐵一樣由機場行出東涌<br />\n屯門果次就由屯門上山行去荃灣<br />\n你地係咪一定要比藉口自己唔再行出去？"},{"pid":"db05ce2a65dc91bdff7314cf2338c4036a86e20f","tid":1647674,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:51:16.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒！所以話啲休息撚on99"},{"pid":"025e87fa15efa421dfab60723b617fbe4728df35","tid":1647674,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:52:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒</span></span>"},{"pid":"80c7c653df439e170f724d2e4cf54a3d20b3086b","tid":1647674,"uid":47169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:53:23.000Z","msg":"好多free rider<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02a712863d358be9f7c75977b6dac1cf068c6e8","tid":1647674,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:58:01.000Z","msg":"錢係好重要 但作唔係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">贖罪卷</span><br />\n死去既手足 受傷既手足 被捕既手足佢地企出唔係為左你捐既錢 佢地係想香港贏<br />\n香港輸左佢地係第一批受清算既人<br />\n之後就係網上買過裝備既人<br />\n最後就係捐過錢既你地 全部野都會留晒底<br />\n當我地輸左 所有機構都要跪<br />\n冇人保得住你地既資料<br />\n私隱？係支共面前根本就係笑話<br />\n今日你再唔企出黎仲諗住等人救既話<br />\n準備好身後事同遺書啦"},{"pid":"d0e53e35198f5c11b9f3e9d0ed50d76005700a54","tid":1647674,"uid":260065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:58:14.000Z","msg":"攬炒"},{"pid":"3fdcc851d8d5ed63c370fe478b11bc075a134ee3","tid":1647674,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:00:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒</span></span>"},{"pid":"85ade0fce10d7fe9e9049c15986f6ac47e34f158","tid":1647674,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,